We visited a union hall in Brisbane or one of the mining towns. Queensland's unions are less factional than down south - it's AWU territory here.

[? if qld_workers_cpa < qld_workers_cpa + 0.005 : We reinforced Labor solidarity and marginalized a few communist agitators. ?]

The Queensland Right dominates the union movement here. This is their stronghold.

