We met with union comrades in Hobart or Launceston. Tasmania's small Labor community means everyone knows everyone.

[? if tas_workers_cpa < tas_workers_cpa + 0.005 : Communist influence is minimal here - Tasmania's unions are solidly Labor. ?]

The Centre faction benefits most from these personal relationships in Australia's smallest state.

@no_visit

We decided not to visit the unions today. Our relationship with organized labor remains unchanged.
